{"tid":1355640,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我明係好開心，但可唔可以唔好何妖洗版","createTime":"2019-07-23T10:46:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T10:53:08.000Z","uid":275865,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"62ff2723d88264011ca63cd753478e9f458edece","tid":1355640,"uid":275865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:46:53.000Z","msg":"成個連登都係何妖<br />\n笑下就算，洗唔洗咁L多個post<br />\n自己諗下咩人帶齊架生可以入村<br />\n去到咁入，拆都要時間，冇人搞佢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1RpUhP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1RpUhP.jpg&h=0bd551cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n琴日何妖爛左兩塊玻璃都馬上鬧，今日拆佢老豆老母個墳佢仲唔出聲？<br />\n<br />\n一係就自編自導自演，一係就真係有人收唔到尾數<br />\n<br />\n何妖傾到七點，好嗎？<br />\n<br />\n724同埋727都未傾好<br />\n我地唔好好似林奠咁對d<span style=\"color: red;\">死物</span>咁大反應啦，好嗎"},{"pid":"99c86942d8c22cd10d290409d9f7e3ba03acf982","tid":1355640,"uid":275865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:47:22.000Z","msg":"仲有上環"},{"pid":"e033df4f86db5cc6b8595bbb2206106b759768bd","tid":1355640,"uid":275865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:47:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cffa383ff08f05e801e47f4fd97cf977fa6c8dd9","tid":1355640,"uid":275865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:47:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cdd1b1c4416fcc43a314b4aa01221520e45eaf44","tid":1355640,"uid":275865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:49:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0790fa385dab16f1d18642fbe051a029fdea5cc9","tid":1355640,"uid":275865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:50:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"90231f4ce9f47808ab574b7b85609080de3ea543","tid":1355640,"uid":275865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:51:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"014a9207d97e0f2c9ede302669fe84f36678b8a0","tid":1355640,"uid":275865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:51:20.